reviews_data.review_text: We love Verb!  So nice to have a Harrisburg location now also. Delicious, smooth coffee and teas. The staff is always friendly and smiling. Give them a try today!
Friendly environment and wonderful coffee!
So happy we finally have a good coffee place in Harrisburg! Super cute, friendly and the coffee is amazing!
SO kind, clean, and yummy!
Great coffee, great service!
My son and I came after school morning drop off and we had such a pleasant experience. The staff is friendly, the menu options delicious. We will be returning!
We absolutely love this verb location! Coffee & a playground has been a really nice place to meet up with friends while the kids play!
Jody was so kind, and the coffee was so good, our kids love the free orange cream slush
We love coming here! The playground is a plus for the littles. 10/10
We love coming here! Great drinks, considerate service, and the playground out back is the main attraction for my kids. Thankful for a place with coffee and something for the kids.
Our favorite coffee shop! Kid friendly and even has a fenced in playground outside for the kids.
Great coffee shop! So friendly, and delicious pastries! My kids loved getting a kids drink and playing on the playground!
Favorite coffee shop with delicious coffee and treats. Very kid friendly!
All these five star reviews are simply confusing. I’ve gave this place three different chances. Coffee is very sweet and bland. Do not recommend.
This place is so cute!!! The coffee was amazing
Great coffee and muffins for the rainy day.
Great coffee and atmosphere!

Wonderful spot ! Came on a rainy day and it was a perfect peaceful spot for coffee and a treat for my kids. Atmosphere was perfect for them to play with the provided toys while
I hung out with friends.
We love it here! Amazing coffee and so kind with great hospitality!
My absolute favorite place!! The best coffee and the best people. Verb knows coffee!!
Outstanding coffee and atmosphere!
Great coffee, close to neighborhood, friendly service! Great with family, meeting up with friends or just stopping by! Love supporting local!
The best coffee shop ever! Great, friendly service. The tastiest coffee! I go here every chance I get! You won’t be disappointed!

reviews_data.review_text:
I scarfed down the coffee and their Earl Grey iced loaf so quickly, I could not even get a picture to share.

I never thought I would describe a pastry as calming but their Earl Grey loaf did just that and was equally as tasty. A 20/10 recommend from me. In addition to their pastry, their coffee is smooth and tasty. The prices are reasonable, too!

You will not be disappointed if you go here for your coffee!
Amazing place!
The Verb has great and friendly service!  The lattes and pastries are delicious!
Very friendly, got the Coconut Matcha Cloud and the Berry & Bee Latte. Very yummy and refreshing on a hot summer day! Will definitely be coming back :)
Love this place! The coffee is delicious. The service is great. And a great place to do work or catch up with a friend!
Love the coffee and service here every time!
Great new coffee shop, friendly service and good coffee, located at the Burg, it’s Verb
I’ve always enjoyed Verb coffee and having this new location closer to home makes it even better! The seasonal lattes are excellent!
Awesome with coffee and playground!
Great service! Great coffee!
incredible service and experience!! i will definitely be back!

I really enjoyed every aspect of Verb coffee. Everything locally made and brewed with fresh ingredients, not pump flavors and beans roasted in another state. The place was clean and comfortable. My tea was fantastic - earl gray with blueberry and lemon on ice. It was a taste of summer!

Met a friend here because it came up on a search and the location was between us, but would not have known about this gem otherwise! (It is connected to The Burg Church, but has its own entrance.) I appreciated the uplifting background music with plenty of seating to relax or work.

I ordered the vanilla black sesame matcha from the seasonal menu and it was delicious! Not too sweet with really nicely balanced flavors. There were several other tempting drinks on the menu and the baked goods looked enticing, though I didn't try one this time. Very friendly service, immaculately clean, lovely views of trees out the windows, and there's even a new playground if you wanted to bring kids along. Definitely worth coming back to visit again.
We love the coffee.  Go check it out, great for getting coffee with the kids. The playground is accessible too!
Great iced sesame matcha and awesome service!
Everyone here is so nice!! Please try the sweet lavender syrup in your drink, it’s a 10/10! Love the atmosphere as well:) they also have a playground for kids to play!
Great atmosphere, great taste. Always coming back for more
Chill and friendly environment. Very peaceful☺️ Excellent service and of course coffee!!
Coffee was great! This is good place for those who need to study!
First time here. Peaceful friendly atmosphere. Staff was knowledgeable and helpful. I brought my 3 year old daughter and she also enjoyed herself. Will definitely be back!
Wonderful service!!
Adorable place and great coffee!!
A friendly coffee spot with some bakery items. Coffee was good and their homemade flavors were nice and not overpowering or too sweet. Would come back!
Best coffee I’ve, which I suppose is no surprise since it is made to God’s glory at this place, I wouldn’t call it “fully redeemed coffee” but it’s pretty close.

Super friendly, and has a new fenced in playground! Inside is quiet and a perfect place to meet with a friend of get some work done. Outside is the perfect place to bring the kids to run around while you enjoy a coffee! Coffee is a 10/10!
Amazing coffee with amazing staff! 100% recommend if you have kiddos too!
Such a nice quaint spot for a quick bite for breakfast. Friendly staff and kid friendly play area out back!!
Such an amazing place!! Amazing drinks and beautiful atmosphere! The barista was super sweet!! Can’t wait to come back! I loved their seasonal matcha!! Amazing decor and aesthetic.
Nice coffee shop with friendly people, quiet atmosphere, and good coffee. We loved that this location has a fenced in playground for the kids!

I came here with a friend because I noticed that it had coffee and a playground for our toddlers. Everyone was welcoming, and it was quiet on a Tuesday morning around 10AM. The playground is fully fenced, and if you’ve got a small child, you know how amazing that is! My friend and I actually got to converse. The coffee was good (Medley Latte) but the flavoring was a little subtle for my taste. I’ll likely try something different next time. The muffin (apple cinnamon) was delicious. We do wish the playground had a little more shade, but will likely just come a bit earlier when it’s cooler out. Overall, great experience and we’ll be back!
What a hidden gem!! Beautiful environment and not crowded at all.
Love the lattes! Great to have a real latte place in the neighborhood. Friendly staff, great sitting/ working area.
Great place with great staff, especially Jody, who are willing to educate you on the coffee beans they have and techniques for steaming milk! They also pull a great shot and make great lattes
First time. Friendly staff and delicious coffee.
A nice small town coffee shop with homemade syrups. Plenty of space to sit and enjoy your coffee and even a playground if you have your kids with you!
noice
yummy

This was such a cute place! I came to meet a friend and had my kids and i had no clue it had a playground! My drink was amazing and my kids loved the blueberry muffin! This wil definitely be a place i return!

I only had coffee.
Great little place off the usual path.
I didn't have any of their baked goods, but locals told me they were excellent and  freshly made.
Very nice staff and cute atmosphere
Grateful for a good matcha and incredible customer service! A uplifting coffee shop— what a treat.
Great cold brew coffee in Harrisburg! Definitely be back!
A great place to get coffee and baked goods! Also plenty of seating and wifi to get work done.
The best coffee shop in the area! Love the coffee and service.
The best of the best! Best baristas and drinks around!
Love this place! Jody is awesome! The food and drinks are delicious and service is wonderful!
Jody is the best. He is so sweet to my friend who has dementia she loves to come see him!
Perfect atmosphere for our church circle to meet! Service is excellent and the coffee is amazing!
Great coffee and atmosphere! Highly recommend!
This is the best place to meet a friend. Lets the kids play, coffee and yummy treats.

Awesome little shop. Throw me off cuz it's attatched to the outside of a church,  but the girl working was really nice & the matcha I got was phenomenal! Highly reccomend and would definitely go back.
Def recommend! Perfect spot for fams with kids (playground in the back) + such a great work spot inside!
Love the Verb and love that it’s located in my wonderful church🥳🥳 everyone’s always super friendly❣️
Haven’t had the food here so I can’t speak to it but the coffee is AMAZING!!!!! I come here at least 2x per week after my workouts
Love this place! Great atmosphere!
Amazing atmosphere
Great service, friendly staff, great vibes, great coffee!
Jody is very friendly and always has a smile. I recommend his beef jerky and common loaf. Will absolutely be back.

Super friendly and welcoming! Top notch service. And my daughter says “I love it so much here. The hot chocolate is the best!” Definitely stop by and if you have kiddos there is a great playground to hang out on while you enjoy your coffee 🥰.
Great coffee, wide open space, and kind costumer service.

This is becoming a favorite coffee spot, whether it's for an outing with my little ones or for a quiet spot to work. Each staff person who has been there when I've come has been so friendly and happy to answer questions to guide my coffee choice. An Americano with the orange blossom syrup is my favorite drink so far. The scent of orange wafting off the cup was just delightful and tasted like a kiss of sweet sunshine!
Moms - The playground on the side of the church is available for kids to play. Just brought my toddler this time with a picnic lunch. I got to enjoy quality coffee and he got to explore a new spot!
I will note that the playground was in full sun around noon in March. So it might get too hot for playing in peak sun hours in the summer. But it looks like it would be shaded again in later afternoon. There are a couple benches and one picnic table with an umbrella.
Last note, you can always go in the main church entrance, which has an ADA (and stroller friendly) ramp. That wasn't clear to me the first time I came and only saw Verb signage at the side door. Parking at the main doors also puts you closer to the ramp and the playground.
Hope you enjoy this sweet spot!
Incredible service! So clean, such a cute place, and the coffee was INCREDIBLE!!

Great spot to sit and hang out. Perfect for remote work during the week because it’s not over crowded or loud. They have some of the great specialty drinks (not too sweet) and if you’re kind of a coffee snob, the coffee itself is the best around.
Great atmosphere! Jody was excellent, providing wonderful service.
Always a great experience at The Verb! Try the Lavender Matcha! So good!
Peaceful place for meeting family and friends or special “Me time”.
The place upon entering is clean and staff was very polite. The menu was great and I look forward to drinking my drink.
Amazing service! Cute coffee shop:)

I’ve had the pleasure to visit Verb Coffee twice, thanks to someone who posted about it in the local Harrisburg FB group. Verb Coffee is attached to the Burg Church with two entrances, one immediately after turning into the lot and one to the rear. The decor is more of a minimalist design; however, it’s very clean and crisp. On my first visit, I ordered an Earl Grey Loaf and a Maple Butter Oatmilk Latte, both were delicious; therefore I visited again today and ordered the exact same thing. Staff has been very friendly and welcoming. It’s a calm and soothing vibe upon entering- I’m not sure if it’s the spiritual aspect of it being connected to a church, the biblical message that greets you once you enter or a combination of it all.

This little quiet spot is definitely worth the visit. Check them out!
Very good service and good people. Love the coffee as well!
The gentleman running the counter was super sweet. I ordered a hot chai and pastry—both were super tasty. I can’t wait to stop by again.
Friendly atmosphere, plenty of seating, and great coffee, teas, and fresh treats!
Wonderful place, warm staff and great service!
Love the iced maple butter latte! Stop in 6am-6pm. Staff is so friendly!
Spacious, open coffee shop. The best pastries which have a rotating selection and I love their seasonal drinks.
Wonderfully quiet atmosphere with the best baristas who aim to please. The coffee is perfect, seating comfie and hours 6a-6p!! Perfect. ❤️
great coffee even more amazing folks serving and hanging out ! Lots of choices for syrups and diet options ! Come grab a cup
Great coffee and great coffee. Love it  🤩
Great quite little place. Service was excellent! Coffee was great!
Love this place!
Cute coffee shop inside a church :)
I truly enjoyed Verb Coffee in Harrisburg . The atmosphere , music ,the coffee ,customer service was 💯 Jodi was so helpful and welcoming . I will be back !

Great local spot! I was super happy they had unsweetened matcha! Not the kind that tastes like a milk shake - I love the vibe, it’s quiet, people were nice and it’s a good space to get some work done.
Great coffee and a clean shop! Good service as well!
What a great place! Clean, peaceful and Jody is an amazing barista. He is professional, courteous, and skilled. Great experience!
Verb at The Burg is a Harrisburg MUST! Service is always great and the atmosphere is perfect for work or leisure.
good coffee close by!!

I usually go to the location in Concord and was so happy to see one open in Harrisburg! It was scrumptious as always and definitely the best cup of coffee around. The staff is always so friendly and the vibe is warm and welcoming.
The best Cortado I had in NC. Their light roasted coffee beans is great. The staff is always welcoming.
Really nice new coffee place in Harrisburg! ... and has a nice outside play area for kids!!
Fantastic coffee. Nice quiet spot. Great location for coffee without having to drive the busy part of 49.
Amazing coffee shop!!! I love the earl grey latte
Welcoming and chill environment. Very nice people and a great place to recharge.
Awesome ambiance and friendly service
Friendly people and coffee that makes a good morning.
Great place for coffee! House made syrups are flavorful without being overpowering or overly sweet. The blueberry muffins are also amazing!
Hands down the best coffee and pastries in Harrisburg!
Best coffee in the city
Having Coffee at the Burg Churches  Verb Coffee! Wonderful coffee with fantastic service! Really peaceful atmosphere to get things done! Do yourself a favor and stop in!!
Nice people but is affiliated with the church. Good syrups!
Appreciated Jodi and his customer service! I would highly recommend this place to anyone! Great atmosphere, awesome staff and lovely place to be with friends, family and significant other!
Lovely Staffa and great coffee!
Great local coffee shop!
Great place
They are the best.  Jody was awesome! Coffee is great.
I walked in and the staff was so kind and welcoming. Answered every questions and provided recommendations. The atmosphere and coffee is unbeatable. Will be back!
Love Verb great coffee in a nice calming atmosphere
What a great hidden gem in Harrisburg NC! Delicious coffee and homemade pastries. I will be back!
Fantastic experience, lovely staff, lovely atmosphere!! So kind and so yummy!!! Definitely will be back!!
Great & varied menu, a fun seasonal menu, knowledgeable barista, & cool vibes (would be a great workspace). Will be returning! ☕️
I just picked up. Red Velvet Latte. Delicious. You gotta try them out
Wonderful coffee shop. The employees are delightful. The coffee is wonderful!!!
Nicole did a great job! Really appreciate a worshipful environment.
Delicious coffee, and even better service.

This coffee shop was all I needed today! I got the seasonal earl Grey latte and it was delicious, not overly sweet like so many other places would make lattes to be. Just the perfect flavor. The space is also very nice, open, therefore great for hanging out, working or studying. I will definitely be back!!

I love Verb Coffee and I am so glad they have opened this new location in Harrisburg!  House made syrups, pastries made fresh in their flagship store, and drinks expertly crafted by kind, knowledgeable baristas.

reviews_data.review_text: Great new coffee shop. Friendly service and quick. The coffee was great too!
Always delicious and friendly staff
I had a matcha that was DELISH!! I worked on schoolwork for about 3 hours and it was so peaceful and quiet! I thoroughly enjoys my experience here and will be back!

We were looking for a local coffee shop around Charlotte and Verb Coffee in Harrisburg, NC didn’t disappoint. We could feel the church-y vibes here, but thankfully it wasn’t religion imposed on us any moment that we were here.

The seating area inside is fairly large, and for a Saturday morning, it wasn’t too busy. The menu is simple and straightforward and the baristas are friendly. We got the chai and the orange blossom coffee, both of which tasted wonderful. The banana bread was divine too!

The parking area outside is big enough. They’re open from Monday to Saturday from 10am-6pm. I highly recommend it. Coffee for the win!
A nice quiet place to get work/school done!
Go visit, great coffee in the ‘burg!!!
Amazing coffee!
My favorite coffee shop, everyone is super nice and coffee is amazing
I’ve been to this coffee shop twice now, and have always received the best service! Everyone is so friendly and helpful when it comes to my dietary restrictions. I love coming here!
A great way to start your morning. Excellent service and a delicious mocha!
Awesome coffee shop and excellent service!
Try the orange blossom latte with oat milk👌🏼
The BEST of the BEST! Great service, great coffee 🩷
Love this coffee shop! This is by far my favorite little place to visit for a great, unique coffee!
The people here are the best. Coffee variety is good too!!
Verb coffee has amazing coffee and service and are always the best addition to my Sunday morning before worship at The Burg!!!

What a perfect little gem! The coffee is great, and the baristas friendly! It’s a quiet place to relax and sip on your coffee, and plenty of room/seating! I also believe they will be opening a playground area for kids soon, where parents can sip while the kids play! Best of both worlds for this momma!
Great place to do work and a great place to hang. Great coffee and great people!
Excellent coffee, and even better people! Service is great. And they have a fantastic mission!
Coffee excellent, atmosphere excellent, very comfortable and relaxing!! Great music
Love this place always clean, staff always inviting,  always professional, drinks always taste to perfection. Highly recommend  to stop by. Did i forget service is super fast!!!
Excellent customer service and the vanilla latte is soooo good. Glad they are in Harrisburg now. 🩷

Coffee is superb; perfectly pulled espresso shot. Delicious house made syrups. The atmosphere is super clean, fresh, and cute. Staff is pleasant and friendly. Adequate seating and table space for working. Easily accessible electrical outlets are also a plus! I've been to almost every coffee shop around Concord, Kannapolis, Harrisburg, Salisbury and even Mooresville and this is easily one of my favorites. Will be back!

Very excited about the Harrisburg location. It’s so cute inside and the coffee is amazing! I ordered an iced vanilla latte - delicious as always, not too sweet or too bitter. The vanilla syrup tastes homemade but I haven’t verified.
An absolute pleasure! The staff was amazing and the drinks were delightful!
Coffee was great as well as the atmosphere! Very good, will come back!
The best coffee! Love that there is a location closer to home!
Excellent service. The drinks hit the spot. The blueberry, lemon, earl Grey tea is FABULOUS and you can only get it at the Harrisburg location.

Verb Coffee is tastefully designed, clean, bright, easy to get to, and most importantly, it has delicious coffee! Each drink was expertly made and tasted of the caliber achieved by an expert barista. I would highly recommend Verb Coffee to anyone looking for:
-great café beverages
-bright, friendly, clean sitting area to work, read, or chat
-warm hospitality with a hopeful perspective
Great coffee and friendly staff.
BEST COFFEE in Harrisburg! If you are looking for an excellent cup of coffee stop by Verb, you won’t be disappointed!
Great vibes, clean restrooms and awesome coffee! Lots of space for big groups too.
Love the atmosphere of this coffee shop!! And the coffee is the best in the area!
Excellent coffee and very friendly staff. I was very impressed!
The best coffee in town!

Great pastries, coffee, chai. Wi-Fi was upgraded nice place to come have coffee and do a little work. Nice change from my work from home setup.
Staff is always welcoming and friendly.
Great place to have a coffee, a sweet treat, all while you work or relax

The best coffee shop!! The coffee and house made syrups are 10/10. It’s a great space to work or just hang out with friends. Very aesthetically pleasing. I love grabbing a coffee on the way into church!!
I love Verb! My family and I come weekly. They have amazing coffee and fun drinks and I love their pastries. Definitely my favorite coffee shop!
Hands down the best lattés and cappuccinos!! Love the vibe here, and the attention to detail is amazing!!

As a coffee lover this place is just what I needed in Harrisburg! The coffee at Verb is amazing with their house made syrups!! And to top it all off they have the best staff! Love this place, I can’t recommend it enough!!
Great place to stop for a breakfast coffee and pastry on your way to work. Fast and delicious!! Homemade pastries 😋

Love that they opened up a micro coffee shop like this, right in the heart of Harrisburg. Their coffee is great, and the atmosphere is extremely welcoming. They have a rotation of homemade syrups for your coffee needs, and a small selection of pastries and grab and go bites.

Highly recommend!

Verb coffee is the perfect environment to do school work and read Gods word . With the cozy atmosphere and the amazing coffee I feel at home and a sense of peace when i come in . The top it all off are the great baristas that welcome me with kindness everyday . I recommend Verb Coffee for everyone! ❤️
Julissa was so nice, made me a delicious vanilla cappuccino! 😊😊

Haven’t had the food here so I can’t speak to it but the coffee is AMAZING!!!!! I come here at least 2x per week after my workouts
Love this place! Great atmosphere!
Amazing atmosphere
Great service, friendly staff, great vibes, great coffee!
Jody is very friendly and always has a smile. I recommend his beef jerky and common loaf. Will absolutely be back.

Super friendly and welcoming! Top notch service. And my daughter says “I love it so much here. The hot chocolate is the best!” Definitely stop by and if you have kiddos there is a great playground to hang out on while you enjoy your coffee 🥰.
Great coffee, wide open space, and kind costumer service.

This is becoming a favorite coffee spot, whether it's for an outing with my little ones or for a quiet spot to work. Each staff person who has been there when I've come has been so friendly and happy to answer questions to guide my coffee choice. An Americano with the orange blossom syrup is my favorite drink so far. The scent of orange wafting off the cup was just delightful and tasted like a kiss of sweet sunshine!
Moms - The playground on the side of the church is available for kids to play. Just brought my toddler this time with a picnic lunch. I got to enjoy quality coffee and he got to explore a new spot!
I will note that the playground was in full sun around noon in March. So it might get too hot for playing in peak sun hours in the summer. But it looks like it would be shaded again in later afternoon. There are a couple benches and one picnic table with an umbrella.
Last note, you can always go in the main church entrance, which has an ADA (and stroller friendly) ramp. That wasn't clear to me the first time I came and only saw Verb signage at the side door. Parking at the main doors also puts you closer to the ramp and the playground.
Hope you enjoy this sweet spot!
Incredible service! So clean, such a cute place, and the coffee was INCREDIBLE!!

Great spot to sit and hang out. Perfect for remote work during the week because it’s not over crowded or loud. They have some of the great specialty drinks (not too sweet) and if you’re kind of a coffee snob, the coffee itself is the best around.
Great atmosphere! Jody was excellent, providing wonderful service.
Always a great experience at The Verb! Try the Lavender Matcha! So good!
Peaceful place for meeting family and friends or special “Me time”.
The place upon entering is clean and staff was very polite. The menu was great and I look forward to drinking my drink.
Amazing service! Cute coffee shop:)

I’ve had the pleasure to visit Verb Coffee twice, thanks to someone who posted about it in the local Harrisburg FB group. Verb Coffee is attached to the Burg Church with two entrances, one immediately after turning into the lot and one to the rear. The decor is more of a minimalist design; however, it’s very clean and crisp. On my first visit, I ordered an Earl Grey Loaf and a Maple Butter Oatmilk Latte, both were delicious; therefore I visited again today and ordered the exact same thing. Staff has been very friendly and welcoming. It’s a calm and soothing vibe upon entering- I’m not sure if it’s the spiritual aspect of it being connected to a church, the biblical message that greets you once you enter or a combination of it all.

This little quiet spot is definitely worth the visit. Check them out!
Very good service and good people. Love the coffee as well!
The gentleman running the counter was super sweet. I ordered a hot chai and pastry—both were super tasty. I can’t wait to stop by again.
Friendly atmosphere, plenty of seating, and great coffee, teas, and fresh treats!
Wonderful place, warm staff and great service!
Love the iced maple butter latte! Stop in 6am-6pm. Staff is so friendly!
Spacious, open coffee shop. The best pastries which have a rotating selection and I love their seasonal drinks.
Wonderfully quiet atmosphere with the best baristas who aim to please. The coffee is perfect, seating comfie and hours 6a-6p!! Perfect. ❤️
great coffee even more amazing folks serving and hanging out ! Lots of choices for syrups and diet options ! Come grab a cup
Great coffee and great coffee. Love it  🤩
Great quite little place. Service was excellent! Coffee was great!
Love this place!
Cute coffee shop inside a church :)
I truly enjoyed Verb Coffee in Harrisburg . The atmosphere , music ,the coffee ,customer service was 💯 Jodi was so helpful and welcoming . I will be back !

Great local spot! I was super happy they had unsweetened matcha! Not the kind that tastes like a milk shake - I love the vibe, it’s quiet, people were nice and it’s a good space to get some work done.
Great coffee and a clean shop! Good service as well!
What a great place! Clean, peaceful and Jody is an amazing barista. He is professional, courteous, and skilled. Great experience!
Verb at The Burg is a Harrisburg MUST! Service is always great and the atmosphere is perfect for work or leisure.
good coffee close by!!

I usually go to the location in Concord and was so happy to see one open in Harrisburg! It was scrumptious as always and definitely the best cup of coffee around. The staff is always so friendly and the vibe is warm and welcoming.
The best Cortado I had in NC. Their light roasted coffee beans is great. The staff is always welcoming.
Really nice new coffee place in Harrisburg! ... and has a nice outside play area for kids!!
Fantastic coffee. Nice quiet spot. Great location for coffee without having to drive the busy part of 49.
Amazing coffee shop!!! I love the earl grey latte
Welcoming and chill environment. Very nice people and a great place to recharge.
Awesome ambiance and friendly service
Friendly people and coffee that makes a good morning.
Great place for coffee! House made syrups are flavorful without being overpowering or overly sweet. The blueberry muffins are also amazing!
Hands down the best coffee and pastries in Harrisburg!
Best coffee in the city
Having Coffee at the Burg Churches  Verb Coffee! Wonderful coffee with fantastic service! Really peaceful atmosphere to get things done! Do yourself a favor and stop in!!
Nice people but is affiliated with the church. Good syrups!
Appreciated Jodi and his customer service! I would highly recommend this place to anyone! Great atmosphere, awesome staff and lovely place to be with friends, family and significant other!
Lovely Staffa and great coffee!
Great local coffee shop!
Great place
They are the best.  Jody was awesome! Coffee is great.
I walked in and the staff was so kind and welcoming. Answered every questions and provided recommendations. The atmosphere and coffee is unbeatable. Will be back!
Love Verb great coffee in a nice calming atmosphere
What a great hidden gem in Harrisburg NC! Delicious coffee and homemade pastries. I will be back!
Fantastic experience, lovely staff, lovely atmosphere!! So kind and so yummy!!! Definitely will be back!!
Great & varied menu, a fun seasonal menu, knowledgeable barista, & cool vibes (would be a great workspace). Will be returning! ☕️
I just picked up. Red Velvet Latte. Delicious. You gotta try them out
Wonderful coffee shop. The employees are delightful. The coffee is wonderful!!!
Nicole did a great job! Really appreciate a worshipful environment.
Delicious coffee, and even better service.

This coffee shop was all I needed today! I got the seasonal earl Grey latte and it was delicious, not overly sweet like so many other places would make lattes to be. Just the perfect flavor. The space is also very nice, open, therefore great for hanging out, working or studying. I will definitely be back!!

I love Verb Coffee and I am so glad they have opened this new location in Harrisburg!  House made syrups, pastries made fresh in their flagship store, and drinks expertly crafted by kind, knowledgeable baristas.

reviews_data.review_text: Great new coffee shop. Friendly service and quick. The coffee was great too!
Always delicious and friendly staff
I had a matcha that was DELISH!! I worked on schoolwork for about 3 hours and it was so peaceful and quiet! I thoroughly enjoys my experience here and will be back!

We were looking for a local coffee shop around Charlotte and Verb Coffee in Harrisburg, NC didn’t disappoint. We could feel the church-y vibes here, but thankfully it wasn’t religion imposed on us any moment that we were here.

The seating area inside is fairly large, and for a Saturday morning, it wasn’t too busy. The menu is simple and straightforward and the baristas are friendly. We got the chai and the orange blossom coffee, both of which tasted wonderful. The banana bread was divine too!

The parking area outside is big enough. They’re open from Monday to Saturday from 10am-6pm. I highly recommend it. Coffee for the win!
A nice quiet place to get work/school done!
Go visit, great coffee in the ‘burg!!!
Amazing coffee!
My favorite coffee shop, everyone is super nice and coffee is amazing
I’ve been to this coffee shop twice now, and have always received the best service! Everyone is so friendly and helpful when it comes to my dietary restrictions. I love coming here!
A great way to start your morning. Excellent service and a delicious mocha!
Awesome coffee shop and excellent service!
Try the orange blossom latte with oat milk👌🏼
The BEST of the BEST! Great service, great coffee 🩷
Love this coffee shop! This is by far my favorite little place to visit for a great, unique coffee!
The people here are the best. Coffee variety is good too!!
Verb coffee has amazing coffee and service and are always the best addition to my Sunday morning before worship at The Burg!!!

What a perfect little gem! The coffee is great, and the baristas friendly! It’s a quiet place to relax and sip on your coffee, and plenty of room/seating! I also believe they will be opening a playground area for kids soon, where parents can sip while the kids play! Best of both worlds for this momma!
Great place to do work and a great place to hang. Great coffee and great people!
Excellent coffee, and even better people! Service is great. And they have a fantastic mission!
Coffee excellent, atmosphere excellent, very comfortable and relaxing!! Great music
Love this place always clean, staff always inviting,  always professional, drinks always taste to perfection. Highly recommend  to stop by. Did i forget service is super fast!!!
Excellent customer service and the vanilla latte is soooo good. Glad they are in Harrisburg now. 🩷

Coffee is superb; perfectly pulled espresso shot. Delicious house made syrups. The atmosphere is super clean, fresh, and cute. Staff is pleasant and friendly. Adequate seating and table space for working. Easily accessible electrical outlets are also a plus! I've been to almost every coffee shop around Concord, Kannapolis, Harrisburg, Salisbury and even Mooresville and this is easily one of my favorites. Will be back!

Very excited about the Harrisburg location. It’s so cute inside and the coffee is amazing! I ordered an iced vanilla latte - delicious as always, not too sweet or too bitter. The vanilla syrup tastes homemade but I haven’t verified.
An absolute pleasure! The staff was amazing and the drinks were delightful!
Coffee was great as well as the atmosphere! Very good, will come back!
The best coffee! Love that there is a location closer to home!
Excellent service. The drinks hit the spot. The blueberry, lemon, earl Grey tea is FABULOUS and you can only get it at the Harrisburg location.

Verb Coffee is tastefully designed, clean, bright, easy to get to, and most importantly, it has delicious coffee! Each drink was expertly made and tasted of the caliber achieved by an expert barista. I would highly recommend Verb Coffee to anyone looking for:
-great café beverages
-bright, friendly, clean sitting area to work, read, or chat
-warm hospitality with a hopeful perspective
Great coffee and friendly staff.
BEST COFFEE in Harrisburg! If you are looking for an excellent cup of coffee stop by Verb, you won’t be disappointed!
Great vibes, clean restrooms and awesome coffee! Lots of space for big groups too.
Love the atmosphere of this coffee shop!! And the coffee is the best in the area!
Excellent coffee and very friendly staff. I was very impressed!
The best coffee in town!

Great pastries, coffee, chai. Wi-Fi was upgraded nice place to come have coffee and do a little work. Nice change from my work from home setup.
Staff is always welcoming and friendly.
Great place to have a coffee, a sweet treat, all while you work or relax

The best coffee shop!! The coffee and house made syrups are 10/10. It’s a great space to work or just hang out with friends. Very aesthetically pleasing. I love grabbing a coffee on the way into church!!
I love Verb! My family and I come weekly. They have amazing coffee and fun drinks and I love their pastries. Definitely my favorite coffee shop!
Hands down the best lattés and cappuccinos!! Love the vibe here, and the attention to detail is amazing!!

As a coffee lover this place is just what I needed in Harrisburg! The coffee at Verb is amazing with their house made syrups!! And to top it all off they have the best staff! Love this place, I can’t recommend it enough!!
Great place to stop for a breakfast coffee and pastry on your way to work. Fast and delicious!! Homemade pastries 😋

Love that they opened up a micro coffee shop like this, right in the heart of Harrisburg. Their coffee is great, and the atmosphere is extremely welcoming. They have a rotation of homemade syrups for your coffee needs, and a small selection of pastries and grab and go bites.

Highly recommend!

Verb coffee is the perfect environment to do school work and read Gods word . With the cozy atmosphere and the amazing coffee I feel at home and a sense of peace when i come in . The top it all off are the great baristas that welcome me with kindness everyday . I recommend Verb Coffee for everyone! ❤️
Julissa was so nice, made me a delicious vanilla cappuccino! 😊😊
